<p>A visitor has requested access to Drynn.</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> {{.Email}}</p>
{{- if .IP}}
<p><strong>Client IP:</strong> {{.IP}}</p>
{{- end}}
{{- if .Reason}}
<p><strong>Reason:</strong></p>
<p>{{.ReasonHTML}}</p>
{{- end}}
<p>Review the request and, if appropriate, send an invitation from the admin console.</p>
